$BR
$BR
a) Determine the European call premium  \{ans_rule(20)\}?
$BR
$BR
$BR
$BR
b) Determine the number of shares of stock that you'll sell \{ans_rule(20)\}?
$BR
$BR
$BR
$BR
c) Determine the amount of money that you'll lend \{ans_rule(20)\}?
$BR
$BR
$BR
$BR
